The paper deals with graphical models for representing preferences, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses algorithms for dominance testing, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper presents a search control rule, which is a topic in multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
